&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lola Blankets is dedicated to creating exceptionally soft products that bring comfort, warmth, and joy to everyday life. As the brand continues to expand across categories, packaging and trim play a critical role in elevating the customer experience, reinforcing brand identity, and supporting successful product launches.&lt;/p&gt;
