&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Lola&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lola Blankets is seeking a highly motivated and detail-oriented Trade Marketing Manager to join our team. This role is crucial in supporting our visual merchandising efforts with key retail accounts, ensuring the Lola Blankets brand is represented effectively and consistently across all in-store and digital platforms. This position requires up to 50% travel and can be based in either New York, NY, or Salt Lake City, UT.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a newly created, high-visibility role that sits at the intersection of brand, sales, and retail operations. As our first dedicated Trade Marketing Manager, you will own the end-to-end brand experience across all wholesale and retail partner channels — from the planogram to the merchandising. You will be the face of Lola Blankets to our retail partners, setting and enforcing the visual and brand standards that make our product unmissable at shelf. This role reports into the Commercial Team and works cross-functionally with Brand, Sales, and Operations.&lt;/p&gt;
